name: To Be With You
description:
"That night he came to me gently. Caress me. Like a stud. Very boyish,” Rahmi smiled in her sleep. "My love for him is great. Except after he presented the results of their meeting.”
The extended family decided that Rahmi had to migrate abroad to improve the economic condition of her household. He was given the full right to decide where to try his fate. Ringgit, real or dollar, is much more valuable than rupiah which stands for zero.
